statements: SELECT * FROM brand_influencer_match;
SELECT brand_id, influencer_id FROM brand_influencer_match;
SELECT audience_location, audience_age_range FROM brand_influencer_match WHERE brand_id = 3;
SELECT influencer_id, audience_age_range FROM brand_influencer_match ORDER BY influencer_id DESC;
SELECT brand_id, COUNT(*) AS total_matches FROM brand_influencer_match GROUP BY brand_id;
SELECT influencer_id, brand_id, audience_age_range, audience_location FROM brand_influencer_match;
SELECT brand_id, influencer_id FROM brand_influencer_match WHERE audience_age_range='18-24';
SELECT brand_id, influencer_id FROM brand_influencer_match WHERE audience_location LIKE 'USA%';
SELECT * FROM brand_influencer_match WHERE brand_id=1;
SELECT influencer_id, audience_location FROM brand_influencer_match WHERE audience_age_range='25-34' AND audience_location='Canada';
SELECT brand_name, industry FROM brand;
SELECT influencer_name, follower_count FROM influencer WHERE follower_count > 10000;
SELECT * FROM brand WHERE industry = 'Fashion' ORDER BY brand_name ASC;
SELECT brand_name, target_audience FROM brand WHERE industry = 'Beauty' ORDER BY target_audience DESC;
SELECT influencer_name, audience_demographics FROM influencer WHERE audience_demographics like '%18-24%' ORDER BY influencer_name;
SELECT brand_name, industry FROM brand WHERE brand_id = 1;
SELECT influencer_name, follower_count FROM influencer WHERE follower_count > 100000;
SELECT brand_name, target_audience FROM brand WHERE industry = 'Fashion';
SELECT influencer_name, audience_demographics FROM influencer WHERE influencer_id = 3;
SELECT brand_name, industry, target_audience FROM brand WHERE target_audience LIKE '%Millennials%';
SELECT name, industry FROM brands;
SELECT id, category, followers_count FROM influencers WHERE followers_count > 10000;
SELECT * FROM audience_demographics WHERE gender='female' ORDER BY age_group DESC;
SELECT name, engagement_rate FROM influencers WHERE category='fashion' LIMIT 5;
SELECT website, industry, name FROM brands WHERE industry='Beauty';
SELECT name, followers_count FROM influencers WHERE followers_count > 10000 ORDER BY followers_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM brands WHERE industry = 'Fashion' ORDER BY name ASC;
SELECT name, category FROM influencers JOIN audience_demographics ON influencers.id = audience_demographics.influencer_id WHERE age_group = '18-24' ORDER BY name ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT industry FROM brands WHERE website IS NOT NULL;

SELECT influencers.name, audience_demographics.gender FROM influencers JOIN audience_demographics ON influencers.id = audience_demographics.influencer_id WHERE audience_demographics.location = 'USA' ORDER BY influencers.name ASC;
SELECT * FROM brands;
SELECT brand_name, industry, location FROM brands WHERE audience_size > 10000;
SELECT brand_name, industry, audience_size FROM brands ORDER BY brand_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM influencers WHERE followers > 50000 ORDER BY engagement_rate ASC;

SELECT i.influencer_name, b.brand_name, b.industry FROM influencers i INNER JOIN brand_influencer_matches m ON i.influencer_id = m.influencer_id INNER JOIN brands b ON m.brand_id = b.brand_id WHERE m.match_score > 0.8;
SELECT * FROM brands;
SELECT brand_name, industry FROM brands ORDER BY brand_name ASC;
SELECT brand_name, audience_size FROM brands WHERE industry = 'Fashion';
SELECT influencer_name, followers, engagement_rate FROM influencers ORDER BY followers DESC;
SELECT b.brand_name, i.influencer_name, m.match_score FROM brands b JOIN brand_influencer_matches m ON b.brand_id = m.brand_id JOIN influencers i ON i.influencer_id = m.influencer_id;
SELECT * FROM Brand;
SELECT brand_name, industry FROM Brand ORDER BY brand_name ASC;
SELECT influencer_name, followers_count FROM Influencer WHERE followers_count > 10000;
SELECT influencer_name, followers_count FROM Influencer ORDER BY followers_count DESC LIMIT 3;

SELECT brand_name, industry, Audience.location FROM Brand JOIN BrandAudienceMatch ON Brand.brand_id = BrandAudienceMatch.brand_id JOIN Audience ON BrandAudienceMatch.audience_id = Audience.audience_id;
